    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Mantispilla sp. undescribed: a. Prothorax, lateral view; b. habitus; d. prothoracic dorsum; e. terminalia, ventral view, arrows indicating inner flanges; f, terminalia caudal. Mantispilla perla: c. Prothorax, lateral view; g. terminalia, caudal view; h. terminalia, dorsal view. Mantispilla hilaris: i. terminalia, dorsal view; j. terminalia, caudal view." ;
